1084
01:26:29,761 --> 01:26:37,487
[SPEAKER_20]: maybe you don't see this big increase from the debt exclusion, maybe you actually are evening out or at least reducing the increase that's coming from that.

1085
01:26:37,527 --> 01:26:47,816
