1433
01:55:24,258 --> 01:55:30,921
[SPEAKER_20]: In terms of the uptick in crime last year, it's still safe to say that crime is significantly down over the last 20, 30 years.

1434
01:55:31,701 --> 01:55:33,342
[SPEAKER_17]: I can tell you that we are a safe community.

1435
01:55:33,362 --> 01:55:36,183
