[SPEAKER_20]: We look at the one year, and we always see what's happening right now.

1441
01:55:49,430 --> 01:55:54,514
[SPEAKER_20]: It's important to think about, at least in this context, I think it's important to think about.

1442
01:55:54,534 --> 01:56:03,060
[SPEAKER_20]: We're much better off than we were 30 years ago today in terms of certain metrics, and that's one of them I think that we should be proud of.

1443
