1458
01:57:33,617 --> 01:57:36,720
[SPEAKER_17]: And so we work a lot closely with the district attorney's office on that.

1459
01:57:37,160 --> 01:57:45,907
[SPEAKER_17]: But you know, when you get agencies like the State Department of Mental Health reaching out and giving you grants to kind of work with that, you know, you're moving in some right direction.

