02:02:36,022 --> 02:02:36,102
[SPEAKER_17]: Um,

1525
02:02:37,933 --> 02:02:44,442
[SPEAKER_17]: being said, no matter what we do, I don't think we're ever going to rid ourselves of traffic complaints, right, because we sit in a very unique position.

1526
02:02:44,502 --> 02:02:49,469
