1527
02:02:49,489 --> 02:02:50,049
[SPEAKER_17]: We're going to have that.

1528
02:02:50,189 --> 02:02:51,812
[SPEAKER_17]: We'll have another further conversation on that.

1529
02:02:53,013 --> 02:02:53,894
[SPEAKER_17]: but it's hard to tell.

1530
02:02:53,954 --> 02:02:54,774
[SPEAKER_17]: Yeah, there's a lot.

1531
