[SPEAKER_17]: There's a lot of what you hear from the outside.

1532
02:02:57,236 --> 02:02:58,697
[SPEAKER_17]: It's what you see in the inside reading.

1533
02:02:58,757 --> 02:03:05,261
[SPEAKER_17]: It's the, it's the, uh, you know, it's how you're reading on the officer's faces and how you're doing and how things have over.

1534
02:03:05,941 --> 02:03:17,048
[SPEAKER_17]: And, you know, I got a good command staff and they update me on how things are going also, because I can't be there 24 seven as much as I feel like I am sometimes, but it's, there's a large part of that, but it's not easy.

1535
02:03:17,108 --> 02:03:18,549
[SPEAKER_17]: It's not really easy to say, okay,

1536
